From a507635935e0229419ac905dbaa186679968c861 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Dana Jansens <danakj@orodu.net>
Date: Sun, 20 Aug 2023 14:46:23 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 05/13] Allow code links and self links callbacks to report
 errors

And pass those errors back up to the md4c parser.
---
 README.md       |   2 +
 src/md4c-html.c | 234 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++------------------
 src/md4c-html.h |  40 +++++++--
 3 files changed, 181 insertions(+), 95 deletions(-)

diff --git a/README.md b/README.md
index e50ba19..acf75bd 100644
--- a/README.md
+++ b/README.md
@@ -15,6 +15,8 @@ This is a fork of [md4c](https://github.com/mity/md4c) for use in
   application to turn into URLs. This allows `[foo]($namespace::ClassName)` to be turned into
   a link to `namespace-classname.html` or whatever suits the application.
 * Moves the callbacks for md4c-html into a structure as we've added a bunch of new callbacks.
+* Allows those callbacks to report errors that flow back up into the md4c parser and terminate
+  parsing.
 
 # MD4C Readme
 
